Today we are here to help clear all your doubts related to our Basic to Advanced Makeup course. 💄

This course will prepare you to become a Professional Makeup Artist. It is designed in such a way that it will help you stand out of crowd. 

In this course, we will clear your concepts related to makeup step by step and give you more clarity about the latest trends in the world of Beauty & Fashion.

In case of any doubts and queries, please feel free to call us on 86556 84676.

Course starts from 20th April 2022.
Course Duration : 2 Months

 What you'll learn :
✅Skin theory
✅Colour theory
✅Product knowledge
✅Bridal makeup 
✅Bridal Hairstyles
✅Western makeup and hairstyles
✅No makeup Look
✅5 styles of Saree Draping

Register now and get ₹5000 discount.
